Package: SSGLM
Type: Package
Title: State Space GLM toolbox for spike train analysis
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2018-10-30
Authors@R: person("Jacob", "Ostergaard", email = "ostergaard@math.ku.dk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The main feature of this toolbox is a marginalized particle filter for inhomogeneous Poisson processes, as used to analyze spike trains.
Depends: R(>= 3.4.0)
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.11.0), signal, Matrix, doParallel, doMC, glmnet
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
Suggests: 
    testthat
